title: Photos: Former Allen QB Kyler Murray on hand to watch the Eagles defeat Hebron, 45-13
text: Former Allen, now Texas A&M, quarterback Kyler Murray shakes hands with offensive lineman Gregory Little (74) on the sidelines at the end of the the first half of a high school football game against Hebron at Eagle Stadium on Friday, Oct. 9, 2015, in Allen. (Smiley N. Pool/The Dallas Morning News)
